January.title: Kakana & Kau Vuata
January.backText:
• Se tiko na Nuqanuqa/Nukanuka ka vakatakilakila ni sa cabe na nuqa
  • Damanu/Tamanu
  • Lagakali, buaniviti, caucau, makosoi
  • Vua ni dawa, wi, maqo, uto, weleti, jaina, tarawau, kavika, painapiu, ivi
  • Draudrau tiko na bele sikau, rourou, ota
  • Matua tiko na dalo ni vuci vakabibi na dalo dina ni viti

January.title: Ika & Sasalu
January.backText:
• Levu na Nuqa (Rabbit fish)
  • Dere neke na Lairo
  • Levu na vivili
  • Vakaluveni na saqa, walu
  • Levu na kaikoso, kukusau, kolakola Tadruku, bosucu, Drose

January.title: Veika e yaco e Uciwai
January.backText:
• Gauna ni Tuna/Duna (drule)
  • Sici – Habihabi, Ohi, Mo’omo’o, o’u
  • Ika ni waidroka – Bali se, Bali Tabua, Bali somo, Yavaya, Malea, Lova

January.title: Itei e rawa ni dau teivaki
January.backText:
• Gauna vinaka ni tei – Dalo ni tana, Dalo ni vuci, Vudi, Jaina, Tivoli
  • Teivaki na bele, rourou, karisi, ota
  • Vakarau na vuci me teivaki

January.title: Draki dau namaki
January.backText: Tekivu me basika na draki se na vula i matumatua

January.title: Teitei ka vakamuria na rama ni vula
January.backText: Matua na tei ni vuci, dalo, bele, rourou me vakamuria na ramani ni vula

February.title: Kakana & Kau Vuata
February.backText:
• Sevu nai tei ni yabaki
  • Keli tiko na Uvi taumada me i sevu
  • Matua tiko na Dalo ni were, Dalo ni tana, Tivoli
  • Tekivu tara na lololo/valevale mai veikau
  • Se na dakua/tahua salusalu
  • Matua e levu na kau vuata – wi, moli, ivi, dawa, moli kana
  • Drau ni dalo, bele, nuve

February.title: Ika & Sasalu
February.backText:
• Levu na vivili kei na sasalu ni waitui – kaikoso, kukusau, kolakola Tadruku, bosucu, drose
  • Levu na voro, malevu, kabatia, kawakawa, donu, soisoi

February.title: Veika e yaco e Uciwai
February.backText:
• Ika ni waidaranu/waidroka – Sesere, Malea, Lova
  • Bali se, Bali Tabua/A’bua
  • Vivili ni waidranu/waidroka – O’hi, Mo’omo’o, Asi

February.title: Itei e rawa ni dau teivaki
February.backText: Gauna ni teivaki ni bele, rourou, Tivoli, Dalo ni tana

February.title: Teitei ka vakamuria na rama ni vula
February.backText: Ni matumatua na vanua, ena matumatua talega na wai

March.title: Kakana & Kau Vuata
March.backText:

  • Matua na vutu, ivi

March.backText:

  • Qari, mana, kuka, qarivasa

  • Lailai na ika
  • Tekivu cabe na Tugadra/U’gadra

March.backText:
• Tawa tiko na wai ena Duana/Tuna

Teitei ka vakamuria na rama ni vula
March.backText: Vakarau na tei ni Uvi, Tivoli, bele

April.title: Kakana & Kau Vuata
April.backText:

  • Se na duruka kei na vico
  • Keli tiko na Uvi leleka
  • Matua na uto
  • Se na dilo

April.backText:

April.backText:

May.title: Kakana & Kau Vuata
May.backText:

  • Se na kavika
  • Bota/Matua Rauva, Via, Yabia

  • Gagi ni Doi – vakatakilakila ni veitosoyaki e wai

May.backText:

  • Cabe na Ogo, Walu, Saqa

May.backText:

  • Mata ba, Yavaya

May.title: Itei e rawa ni dau teivaki
May.backText:
• Tei’vu
  • Tekivu me samaki/tavaki na were ni yabaki

May.title: Draki dau namaki
May.backText: Vula i Biri Laca – draki batabata mamaca

May.title: Teitei ka vakamuria na rama ni vula

  • Se na vadra, vasili
  • Matua/Bota na Kawai, Drove/Drose, Cago, Ginger

July.backText:

  • Levu na Ose, daniva, Ogo, Saqa, Walu
  • Vakayaloka na vonu

July.backText:

August.title: Veika e yaco e Uciwai
August.backText:

August.title: Itei e rawa ni dau teivaki
August.backText: Tei na uvi, kawai, bele, rourou, Tavola

September.backText:

  • Se na maqo, drala, wadamu
  • Se na buaniviti, mokosoi

  • Sola na Via

September.backText:
